As a result of the Black Moon Incident, contact has been lost with 64% of Foundation locations, with an unknown number of facilities uninhabitable or devoid of function. 
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[row]]
[[cell style="font-weight:bold;padding: .45em .45em; text-align: left; border-top: 0px solid navy;
