**Response:** ORACLE.AIC suggested the construction of hydroponic farms. In the interim until facilities are built, civilian diets within Global Reconstruction Effort encampments are to be supported by controlled lapses in the containment of SCP-871.

**Outcome:** Construction of hydroponic farms commences, as does the use of SCP-871 to feed surviving populations. 

**Update:** Through unknown means, all instances of SCP-871 have been infected with the Black Blight , leading to outbreaks of the disease in civilian populations across 5 encampments. On ORACLE's recommendation, the anomaly has been neutralised.

Deficiencies in food supply are to be remedied by the recycling of matter from expired civilians. Expiry must not be related to Black Blight. Process fully automated by SCP-7070-1.
[[/cell]]
[[/row]]
[[/table]]
