For Foundation containment and reconstruction efforts to continue, the Foundation requires more man-power. The drafting civilians, or carrying out operations inside fallout encampments, is disallowed under Global Reconstruction Effort agreements. Potential resources of all types are limited. Design a go-forward strategy prioritising the Foundation's continued growth and stability.
