The Foundation has been covertly approached by the following representatives from within the Global Reconstruction Effort: 
* Vincent Anderson Jr., CEO of Anderson Robotics (GoI-1115).
* Lenora Dark, Heir to the Marshall, Carter and Dark fortune (GoI-012).
* D.C. Al Fine, Under-Secretary-General of the United Nations Global Occult Coalition (GoI-007).

All representatives suggested the pooling of organizational resources into the hands of the Foundation, as they were concerned with the overall power and capability of the Global Reconstruction Effort.
