**Response:** ORACLE.AIC deemed the offers of Anderson and Dark to be agreeable and of a net benefit to the Foundation. However, it stated that the goals and strategic aims of integrated GOC members will deviate to the point of organizational schism, unless they are forcibly indoctrinated. Military conflict between resulting factions is likely in 63.21% of generated scenarios.

**Outcome:** Both Anderson Robotics and Marshall, Carter and Dark were incorporated into the Foundation. The Global Occult Coalition’s offer was rejected.
