Upon arrival, the field team encountered a group of 63 human survivors inhabiting a makeshift encampment. At the center of the encampment, the team discovered a formerly contained anomaly, SCP-173, albeit displaying little of its prior documented anomalous properties. Since rediscovery and recontainment, the statue has not moved.

